com.interpss.core.aclf.hvdc

Interface ThyConverter

  • All Superinterfaces:
    com.hazelcast.nio.serialization.DataSerializable, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    Inverter, Rectifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    InverterImpl, RectifierImpl, ThyConverterImpl

    public interface ThyConverter
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, com.hazelcast.nio.serialization.DataSerializable
    A representation of the model object 'Thy Converter'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Firing Ang
    • Firing Ang Limit
    • NBridges
    • Dc Voltage
    • Ac Voltage
    • Power Demand
    • Power Factor Angle
    • Ac Rated Voltage
    • Commuting Z
    • Xformer Ratio
    • Xformer Tap Setting
    • Xformer Tap Step Size
    • Xformer Tap Limit
    • Commuting Capacitor
    • Xfr From Id
    • Xfr To Id
    • Xfr Cir Id
    See Also:
    HvdcLinePackage.getThyConverter()
